- You'll carry it.

11:42.594 --> 11:44.863
Okay, where are you
going to carry it?

11:44.897 --> 11:46.465
You want to wear it?

11:46.498 --> 11:51.203
- Yeah, 'cause I'm cold.
- 'Cause you're cold?

11:54.973 --> 11:59.211
You're beautiful!

11:59.244 --> 12:00.479
