in here make yourself known.

25:13.405 --> 25:15.307
Oh my gosh, what is that?

25:15.341 --> 25:17.276
Bill, are you home?

25:17.309 --> 25:20.813
Oh wow,
if he is he's not happy.

25:26.418 --> 25:27.920
I don't want to be
doing paperwork

25:27.953 --> 25:29.788
and I don't want to
find out what the source

25:29.822 --> 25:31.290
of that smell is,
so let's get out of here

25:31.323 --> 25:33.325
and do not look in
that wood stove.

25:33.359 --> 25:36.829
Leave it for investigators,
let's go.

25:36.862 --> 25:38.898
What are you doing this weekend?

25:38.931 --> 25:42.101
Not coming anywhere near
the river, how about you?

25:50.776 --> 25:53.412
That's it, I'm going.

25:53.445 --> 25:55.915
- Where?
- Los Angeles.

25:55.948 --> 26:00.019
I'm gonna find my real dad.

26:00.052 --> 26:01.320
I thought you didn't need a dad.

26:01.353 --> 26:03.222
I don't.

26:03.255 --> 26:07.293
I'm just gonna haul up with him
until I figure things out.

26:07.326 --> 26:09.061
Can I come?

26:09.094 --> 26:10.996
I've always wanted
to see the ocean.

26:11.030 --> 26:13.299
And I've always wanted
to have a real dad.

26:13.332 --> 26:17.803
And LA has both.

26:17.836 --> 26:18.971
If you don't slow me.

26:19.004 --> 26:20.506
No, no, no, I won't slow you.

26:20.539 --> 26:22.007
I promise.

26:22.041 --> 26:24.810
Cross my heart.

26:24.843 --> 26:26.378
Don't you want that?

26:26.412 --> 26:30.349
Only packing these things.

26:30.382 --> 26:32.785
There's more kinds of things
useful here.

26:32.818 --> 26:35.154
You're brining a CD?

26:35.187 --> 26:38.958
It has the address in it.

28:20.559 --> 28:23.095
And even should she forget,

28:23.128 --> 28:28.167
I will not forget.

28:28.200 --> 28:29.636
Now isn't that a nice...

29:46.011 --> 29:47.579
I need $450.

29:47.613 --> 29:50.983
More like 200 bucks.

29:53.619 --> 29:57.690
These snap-ons
are worth 500 alone.

29:57.724 --> 29:59.491
Well, really,
you're not old enough to pawn

29:59.525 --> 30:01.527
or sell anything,
so you get 50 bucks.

30:01.560 --> 30:04.430
Take it or leave it.

30:08.668 --> 30:10.969
Fine.

30:11.003 --> 30:14.039
You got ripped off.

30:14.072 --> 30:15.607
Those snap-ons were $500 alone.

30:15.642 --> 30:20.179
Shut up and look out the window!

30:25.652 --> 30:28.320
I kind of get it
but I kind of don't.

30:28.353 --> 30:31.023
Why don't you want a dad?

30:31.056 --> 30:32.759
Did you meet Bill?

30:32.792 --> 30:34.727
There's more kinds of dads
then just Bills.

30:34.761 --> 30:36.161
Dads are boys.

30:36.195 --> 30:37.730
And there are two kinds of boys.

30:37.764 --> 30:40.299
Stupid boys and pigs.

30:40.332 --> 30:42.568
There's more than
just boys and pigs.

30:42.601 --> 30:45.404
Things that grow are supposed
to grow into something.

30:45.437 --> 30:47.707
