to grow into bacon,

30:47.740 --> 30:49.374
boys supposed to grow into men.

30:49.408 --> 30:50.710
Like Bruce Springsteen.

30:50.743 --> 30:52.411
Pigs don't grow into bacon.

30:52.444 --> 30:53.646
They get cut into bacon.

30:53.680 --> 30:55.314
They grow themselves.

30:55.347 --> 30:57.784
They're for bacon.

30:57.817 --> 30:59.384
Hitler grew into a man.

30:59.418 --> 31:01.688
Just growing
doesn't make you good.

31:01.721 --> 31:03.790
Well...

31:03.823 --> 31:06.525
you've gotta grow right
like apples.

31:06.558 --> 31:09.729
Good apples are red
and shiny and crunchy.

31:09.762 --> 31:12.231
Bad apples are mushy and brown.

31:12.264 --> 31:14.466
Old as apples.

31:14.500 --> 31:18.437
What makes a man crunchy?

31:23.442 --> 31:27.112
Well, it's how he does.

31:27.145 --> 31:30.382
Always picks you up
when you fall

31:30.415 --> 31:31.818
and he lets you
walk way in front

31:31.851 --> 31:34.586
but he's never far behind.

31:34.620 --> 31:36.756
And when somebody
makes fun of your legs

31:36.789 --> 31:41.393
he'll whisper in your ear
that you're pretty.

31:43.730 --> 31:45.765
And he always makes
his words come true

31:45.798 --> 31:50.269
and doesn't say them
if he can't.

33:07.814 --> 33:08.881
Come on!

33:08.915 --> 33:10.883
Selma.

33:10.917 --> 33:14.821
Shut up.

33:21.694 --> 33:24.596
We're out of gas
and food and money.

33:24.631 --> 33:25.665
Why don't we just
turn ourselves in?

33:25.698 --> 33:33.605
Shut up or I'll rip your
stupid runny mouth off.

33:33.640 --> 33:38.176
Go, go, go.

33:38.210 --> 33:40.345
- You're just gonna leave...
- Come on, go, go, go.

33:40.379 --> 33:44.349
Okay, I'm going.

33:52.557 --> 33:55.695
So I guess we're walking.

33:57.529 --> 34:00.365
Stop!

34:00.399 --> 34:03.602
