happen out here.

34:03.636 --> 34:08.206
Selma.

34:10.910 --> 34:13.278
We'll hop a train
in the morning.

34:19.952 --> 34:21.520
We gotta go back.

34:21.553 --> 34:23.588
Turn ourselves in

34:23.622 --> 34:25.390
and maybe they'll take us
to the orphanage

34:25.424 --> 34:28.593
and it will be all okay.

34:28.628 --> 34:30.328
- Get some sleep.
- No, no, no.

34:30.362 --> 34:31.698
I'm not sleeping here.

34:31.731 --> 34:33.766
Ow.

