about mommies and daddies

35:15.307 --> 35:17.643
and how good they are.

35:17.677 --> 35:19.578
Remind me to tell you something

35:19.611 --> 35:23.548
about mommies and daddies.

35:30.757 --> 35:34.727
They don't want us.

35:53.079 --> 35:57.549
Ain't no one ever stick
their necks out for me.

36:30.783 --> 36:32.051
Get up, get up,
get up, come on.

36:32.084 --> 36:34.954
Get up.

36:34.987 --> 36:38.423
Jo.

36:38.456 --> 36:39.992
Please.

36:40.026 --> 36:43.062
Get up, get up.

36:43.095 --> 36:46.398
Wait no, no.

36:46.431 --> 36:52.071
No, don't leave me, please.

36:52.104 --> 36:55.507
No!

37:17.663 --> 37:20.398
I'm sorry.

37:20.432 --> 37:23.970
I'm sorry.

37:24.003 --> 37:26.438
Jo, I'm sorry.

37:26.471 --> 37:31.576
Next time you slow me
I won't come back for you.

37:41.654 --> 37:45.091
What now?

38:16.188 --> 38:20.192
What's so bad about foster care?

38:20.226 --> 38:25.463
I'm done being a...

