says Colorado,

39:17.717 --> 39:20.119
doesn't mean
he's going to Colorado.

39:36.568 --> 39:39.038
Did you try the door maybe?

39:39.071 --> 39:42.908
Nobody's gonna leave
their doors unlocked.

41:18.304 --> 41:24.310
I used to be afraid
of heaven when I was younger.

41:24.343 --> 41:29.215
Something that never stops.

41:29.248 --> 41:34.253
Wouldn't it get boring?

41:34.286 --> 41:41.260
I don't know,
I guess I was just scared.

41:41.293 --> 41:47.133
But one day, I waited
till the sun started setting

41:47.166 --> 41:51.904
and I looked straight at him
and he looked straight at me.

41:51.937 --> 41:54.373
And I knew...

41:54.406 --> 41:57.776
I could stay here forever

41:57.810 --> 42:01.280
if my real dad was there.

42:07.820 --> 42:11.757
You done?

42:16.462 --> 42:20.132
Heaven ain't real.

42:40.319 --> 42:44.056
Wake up.

43:47.386 --> 43:50.022
I hope you're happy.

43:50.055 --> 43:53.359
Yeah, I'm happy.

44:30.396 --> 44:33.565
It's better.

44:59.591 --> 45:04.363
Preggers.

45:04.396 --> 45:08.400
Where's my gob?

45:08.434 --> 45:11.970
