over a stupid pastry.

46:12.164 --> 46:13.265
Donnie!

46:13.298 --> 46:18.671
Don't say words.

46:19.972 --> 46:22.007
You running?

46:22.040 --> 46:23.509
I don't mean anything by it.

46:23.542 --> 46:27.246
